-07T21:44:59.531Z","comments_closed?":false,"facebook_team?":false,"team_private?":false,"vulnerability_information":"To rate-limit users, you use an old CAPTCHA method that has been broken for quite a while due to developments in OCR. There are many services that are available to quickly solve these and so it offers no protection.\n\nFor example, here is one site that offers easy CAPTCHA breaking: http://captchabot.com/en/\n\nTo prevent brute-force attacks, you should use a newer human verification method. I would recommend Google's \"reCAPTCHA\", which was switched to after the previous one (the one that you use) was broken. You can download it here: https://www.google.com/recaptcha/intro/index.html.","vulnerability_information_html":"\u003cp\u003eTo rate-limit users, you use an old CAPTCHA method that has been broken for quite a while due to developments in OCR. There are many services that are available to quickly solve these and so it offers no protection.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eFor example, here is one site that offers easy CAPTCHA breaking: \u003ca title=\"http://captchabot.com/en/\" href=\"/redirect?url=http%3A%2F%2Fcaptchabot.com%2Fen%2F\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003ehttp://captchabot.com/en/\u003c/span\u003e\u003ci class=\"icon-external-link\"\u003e\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eTo prevent brute-force attacks, you should use a newer human verification method. I would recommend Google\u0026#39;s \u0026quot;reCAPTCHA\u0026quot;, which was switched to after the previous one (the one that you use) was broken. You can download it here: \u003ca title=\"https://www.google.com/recaptcha/intro/index.html\" href=\"/redirect?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Frecaptcha%2Fintro%2Findex.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003ehttps://www.google.com/recaptcha/intro/index.html\u003c/span\u003e\u003ci class=\"icon-external-link\"\u003e\u003c/i\u003